  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nWhen entering a value in the Recipient address, the buttons \"Done\" and \"add to favorites\" display.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/224810/94927807-290a9980-0499-11eb-8413-655e299d6762.png)\r\n\r\nBut when  the input element losses the focus, the buttons disappear. \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/224810/94927778-1e500480-0499-11eb-9b69-138ba6635bfe.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n\"Done\" and \"Add to favorites\" should be visible whenever a valid wallet is entered in the Recipient address\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\"Done and \"Add to favorites\" are hidden but there is a valid address in the input of Recipient.\r\n\r\n#### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nRules for the future PR to be accepted.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: 1.7.0\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n",
